{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"43612-mother-call-that-bird","title":"Mother, Call that Bird!","description":"A little child asks her mother to help her adopt a bird.","language":"English","langCode":"en","isRtl":false,"level":"1","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Alisha Berger"],"illustrators":["Krishnagopal Shreshtha"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"Room to Read","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/43612-mother-call-that-bird"},"cover":{"card":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/99534/size3/5f965f2bff43145b1f5f996e90b44970.jpg","large":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/99534/size6/5f965f2bff43145b1f5f996e90b44970.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/79731/size6/d6b13752d5e271de562de7a3220f4739.jpg","text":"Mother! Please call the bird that lives on that tree.","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/79739/size6/2f668fd82e303c392e2278221812457b.jpg","text":"Mother! Please throw the bird some grains so that it comes to us.","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/79738/size6/b64b84b2074cfe324d4404b86a51d255.jpg","text":"Mother! I want see how the bird eats the grains.","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/79734/size6/a221840ce3767078f7a5cdd92b566242.jpg","text":"Mother! How will she land on her feet?","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/79741/size6/ae2d89e7d7c8150dc0df945f869276d8.jpg","text":"Mother! How will she walk on the ground?","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/79737/size6/ad5a72ec3b72ee2ca0503f92e247c527.jpg","text":"Mother! The bird might be thirsty, let's put out some water for her.","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/79743/size6/e4e13d04dc62a42f1dfa02eb5bf6dc77.jpg","text":"Mother! The bird is so beautiful.","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/79742/size6/10b268eac16d2e869b93b65f162b0436.jpg","text":"Mother! I want to listen to her song.","words":null},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/79745/size6/5f5fe30459802a7c85930e2af7074f48.jpg","text":"Mother! I want to see how she dances.","words":null},{"n":10,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/79746/size6/2bcd0b7e6f9c3cb44ff8c0c159a2444a.jpg","text":"Mother! I want to play with the bird.","words":null},{"n":11,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/79747/size6/a1c4d1e95956def351f6a482c2e6631b.jpg","text":"Mother! Let's make a swing for her, with a string.","words":null},{"n":12,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/79748/size6/3cce5d5ef56ed75a8f383f32acb52da9.jpg","text":"Mother! The bird's feet are bare. Let's give her shoes.","words":null},{"n":13,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/79749/size6/00519f90d1a65ae2a788e24f3ee23bde.jpg","text":"Mother! The bird has no clothes. Let's sew clothes for her.","words":null},{"n":14,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/79750/size6/594165afa8538d2b61adbb4ff27b69ab.jpg","text":"Mother! The bird is my friend.","words":null},{"n":15,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/79751/size6/18fb1ba4231a43380309193b66f35788.jpg","text":"Mother! Please, tell the bird to stay with us forever.","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":15,"words":139}}